{"tid":1611683,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【中共70年】王祖藍、黃金寶現身花車 李亞男：等寶寶長大告訴她","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T09:09:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a6f47f45d7e2b2e5aa6c1102401417f0c1e3f1","tid":1611683,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"中共建政70周年，北京天安門在閱兵儀式後舉行巡遊活動，在「一國兩制」方陣的花車上，有眼利網民發現廣西政協委員、香港藝人王祖藍的身影，站在其旁邊則是有「亞洲車神」稱號的單車名將黃金寶。 <br />\n<br />\n王祖藍今早7時22分已在個人微博貼上一張展示五星紅旗的相片，並寫上：「慶祝中華人民共和國成立70周年！祝福祖國繁榮昌盛，國泰民安！」王祖藍的妻子李亞男也在微博下留言回應：「等寶寶長大，我會告訴她，他的爸爸是多麼的厲害，多麼的讓我們驕傲。」<br />\n<br />\n王祖藍的帖文獲得逾22.4萬人點讚，有網民大讚：「王祖藍是香港唯一代表的藝人，實有太有面子，已走向人生巔峯了。」另有網民寫道：「王祖藍真的將歡樂寫在了臉上，為祖國慶生的激動溢出屏幕。」「祖藍哥愛國愛港。」「中華文化和一國兩制！都是代表，有心啦。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191001/large/1569925007_8fb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191001%2Flarge%2F1569925007_8fb2.jpg&h=2b1fcdc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191001/60105412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191001%2F60105412&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdOu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=38616c8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191001%2F60105412&h=7ed763c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191001/60105412</a>"},{"pid":"b9d2a4b0f5d39a26b33e18ef058dc1e036618ecd","tid":1611683,"uid":301523,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"搵隻專扮女人既醜男上去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b30cd8452b863e32b3424ebbc00101c486ea28"